About coffee, rum, cigars, the Sierra Maestra Mountains, the Bay of Pigs and the Island of Isla de Pinos, about the Tropicana cabaret, the sanctuary of the Cuban patroness Caridad del Cobre, about the Santeria, an African religion to which the descendants of slaves could confess about many of these pages.
